OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRich oil states should pay 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fclimate tax, says Brown    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The world's richest oil states should  
OL,6, pay a global windfall tax to help      
OL,7, poorer nations combat climate change,  
OL,8, ex-PM Gordon Brown has said.           
OL,10,FHe said countries such as Saudi Arabia,
OL,11,Fthe UAE, Qatar and Norway benefited    
OL,12,Ffrom a "lottery style bonanza" last    
OL,13,Fyear, as the price of oil soared.      
OL,15,FMr Brown argues a $25bn (#20.4bn) levy 
OL,16,Fwould boost prospects of a deal on a   
OL,17,Fclimate fund for poorer countries.     
OL,19,FHis intervention comes ahead of the    
OL,20,FCOP28 summit in Dubai in November.     
